      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle is a straightforward budget-friendly option for anyone looking for affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and is being offered in as-is condition, but it still presents real value for the right buyer who wants dependable basics without a big upfront cost. If you\u2019ve been searching for an inexpensive way to get on the road, this is a practical choice worth a look.",
