      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car being sold as-is and priced with that in mind. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it could be a great budget runabout, a project, or a handy parts car for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. If you want something cheap with potential and prefer a straightforward seller, this could be worth a look. Sensibly priced to move.",
