      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Project-ready and priced to move, this car offers solid enthusiast potential with a willing powertrain, usable chassis, and the kind of straightforward mechanical package that makes a great budget build or daily-driver rehab. It shows its age cosmetically and needs attention in the usual areas, but it still presents as a complete, honest car with good parts value and plenty of upside for someone who knows their way around a toolbox. If you want an affordable entry point with real fix-and-drive potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
